summary: An Ordinance authorizing, empowering and directing the Mayor and City Comptroller and ex-officio City Clerk to, in the name of and behalf of The City of Seattle, enter into an indenture of deed with the Puget Sound Electric Railway, a corporation, affecting portions of Lots Seven (7) and Eight (8), Block One (1), Sprague's Addition, and Lots One (1) to Ten (10) inclusive, Block Seven (7), Queen Addition to the City of Seattle, and declaring an emergency.
